				<baseName xml:lang="en">Softener</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">柔软剂</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">Water softener; Magnetic water softener</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">Water softener; Magnetic water softener</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">Materials production</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Organic chemicals</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">A softener, specifically a water softener, is a device that reduces the hardness of water by removing minerals such as calcium and magnesium that cause hard water. This process can prevent damage to appliances, reduce dryness of hair and skin, and prevent buildup on kitchen and bathroom surfaces. Softeners are beneficial for those with high-sodium diets who need to eliminate hard water but don't want to reduce mineral intake. They can also improve the softness and vitality of hair by removing harsh minerals.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">软水器，特别是水软化器，是一种通过去除造成硬水的钙、镁等矿物质来降低水硬度的设备。这一过程可以防止电器损坏，减少头发和皮肤干燥，防止厨房和浴室表面积垢。软水器对那些需要去除硬水但又不想减少矿物质摄入量的高钠饮食者非常有益。软水器还能去除刺激性矿物质，改善头发的柔软度和活力。</common:generalComment>
